---
/**
 * Three-column expertise block with horizontal dividers (iO pattern)
 * "Driven by experience, powered by expertise"
 */
---

<section class="section-spacing">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-16">
      Driven by expertise, powered by local knowledge
    </h2>

    <!-- Three columns separated by vertical rules -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-0">
      <!-- Column 1 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] pt-8 pr-0 md:pr-8 pb-8 md:border-r md:border-r-[var(--color-surface-border)]">
        <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-[28px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-4">
          Knowledge that keeps your business ahead
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
          China's digital landscape evolves rapidly. We track emerging trends, platform changes, and regulation updates so you stay competitive behind the Great Firewall.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] pt-8 px-0 md:px-8 pb-8 md:border-r md:border-r-[var(--color-surface-border)]">
        <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-[28px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-4">
          Focused on data and results
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
          Data drives everything we do together. You get transparent insights, clear metrics, and continuous optimisation that transforms collaboration into measurable results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] pt-8 pl-0 md:pl-8 pb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-[28px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-4">
          Continuous growth, together
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
          Your business goals don't stand still, and neither do we. We evolve with your challenges, adapt to market changes, and proactively improve results through every collaboration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
